    <item>
      <title>埃及在价值 350 亿美元的土地交易后获得阿联酋的第一笔付款</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-28/egypt-has-received-part-of-35-billion-in-uae-funds-sisi-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[埃及已收到阿拉伯联合酋长国承诺的 350 亿美元资金的第一笔转账，这是一笔巨额融资，将使货币更接近贬值，并应释放更多国际援助。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-28/egypt-has-received-part-of-35-billion-in-uae-funds-sisi-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 11:33:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>研究表明，人工智能聊天机器人尚未为选举黄金时段做好准备</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-27/ai-chatbots-not-ready-for-election-prime-time-study-shows</link>
      <description><![CDATA[今年有 50 多个国家举行全国选举，一项新研究显示，人工智能聊天机器人的兴起给选民传播虚假、误导或有害信息带来了风险。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-27/ai-chatbots-not-ready-for-election-prime-time-study-shows</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 27 Feb 2024 20:11:01 GMT</pubDate>
